title: Kaette Kudasai, Akutsu-san! (Please Go Home, Akutsu-san!)

Will she do something horrible to him behind closed doors or will he chase her out? But dealing with Akutsu-san's sexy, cute behavior in such a confined space... heâ€™s sure to get flustered! He wants her to go home, but he also doesn't?
